1
00:00:11,340 --> 00:00:17,640
He carried our sins on that rugged tree

2
00:00:18,660 --> 00:00:24,080
To win our pardon and our victory

3
00:00:24,080 --> 00:00:30,720
In jars of clay we carry the news

4
00:00:30,720 --> 00:00:37,320
Christ is risen, grace has broken through

5
00:00:37,320 --> 00:00:43,560
No condemnation now is ours to dread

6
00:00:44,080 --> 00:00:49,620
By Your Word the faintest soul is fed

7
00:00:49,620 --> 00:00:56,380
We have believed and so we loudly speak

8
00:00:56,380 --> 00:01:02,580
The name of Jesus strength unto the weak

9
00:01:02,580 --> 00:01:09,180
We do not hope in what is seen

10
00:01:09,180 --> 00:01:15,040
But cling to Christ our certainty

11
00:01:15,040 --> 00:01:21,740
The weight of glory yet to come

12
00:01:21,740 --> 00:01:28,160
It's the song of heaven now begun

13
